I usually play only one champion per role, and they&#039;re champions that no one ever bans and RARELY ever play.
I should be able to set &quot;auto lock-in&quot; for my champions when I &quot;declare intention&quot;, then if no one bans or picks the champion before it&#039;s your turn to choose, you will automatically lock in the champion.

